                    ->  Hash Join  (cost=77.50..216.30 rows=4581 width=19) (actual time=2.412..5.299 rows=4581 loops=1)
                          Hash Cond: (i.film_id = f.film_id)
                          ->  Seq Scan on inventory i  (cost=0.00..75.81 rows=4581 width=8) (actual time=0.014..0.817 rows=4581 loops=1)
